Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.56,Default,PAm,0,0,0,,打开四号门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.27,Default,PAm,0,0,0,,重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.94,Default,PAf,0,0,0,,2 号到 5 号　采取 γ 四重奏队形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.27,Default,PAf,0,0,0,,重复一遍　采取 γ 四重奏队形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.18,Default-Top,PAf,0,0,0,,现在各机 FRANXX 状态一切良好{all green}
