Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.09,Default,196,0,0,0,,就算说让我们应对...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.18,Default,556,0,0,0,,这么大的家伙要怎么才能阻止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.14,Default,326,0,0,0,,光是阻止的话是没意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:32.14,Default,326,0,0,0,,不打倒它的话　它就会突破墙壁　我们就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.73,Default,214,0,0,0,,和鹤望兰配合的话应该能有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.86,Default,390,0,0,0,,嗯　也只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.82,Default,666,0,0,0,,要怎么打都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.99,Default,666,0,0,0,,总之让他们看到　只靠我们 13 部队就可以搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.24,Default,16,0,0,0,,明白　交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.24,Default,15,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.66,Default,15,0,0,0,,鹤望兰保持原位不动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.62,Default,666,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.62,Default,214,0,0,0,,光靠我们是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.00,Default,196,0,0,0,,莓　你有什么计划吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.88,Default,15,0,0,0,,鹤望兰只需要给出最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.67,Default,666,0,0,0,,现在不是保留实力的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.96,Default,56,0,0,0,,冷静　兽目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.51,Default,56,0,0,0,,能攻击到那个大家伙核心的只有鹤望兰的长枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.64,Default,15,0,0,0,,五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.31,Default,56,0,0,0,,所以我们创造出一个空隙给鹤望兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.89,Default,56,0,0,0,,你是这么想的吧？莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.98,Default,15,0,0,0,,呃　嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.40,Default,56,0,0,0,,让他们见识见识我们的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.90,Default,666,0,0,0,,好　既然如此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.03,Default,56,0,0,0,,广　你听到了吧？最后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.95,Default,16,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.37,Default,15,0,0,0,,13 部队　作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.16,Default,15,0,0,0,,谢谢　五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.99,Default,56,0,0,0,,现在先集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.87,Default,15,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.50,Default,666,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.71,Default,666,0,0,0,,我们上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.71,Default,390,0,0,0,,坚持住　你不是男子汉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.34,Default,666,0,0,0,,你才是要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.63,Default,390,0,0,0,,当然　我才不想再被说成是拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.97,Default,556,0,0,0,,太司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.05,Default,196,0,0,0,,无论如何都要给鹤望兰创造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.22,Default,326,0,0,0,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.19,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling 疼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.48,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,但是不把那家伙打倒的话是没法结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.61,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,你能行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.86,Default,16,0,0,0,,是的　毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.04,Default,15,0,0,0,,广！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:18.75,Default,56,0,0,0,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.67,Default,16,0,0,0,,一击就了结它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.18,Default,16,0,0,0,,给我进去！{再议}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.40,Default,16,0,0,0,,成功了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.04,Default,15,0,0,0,,广！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.11,Default,15,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.86,Default,15,0,0,0,,广！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.18,Default,PA,0,0,0,,代号 002 与代号 016 间的连接中断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.88,sign_monitor,PA,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fax0.2\frz7.058\c&H2587DF&\blur0.7\pos(1428.4,914.8)}鸡冠苋\N\h 寄容状态监视系统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.88,sign_monitor,PA,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fax0.05\blur0.7\c&H2A8DE0&\b1\pos(52.4,74.8)\frz358.2}鹤望兰\N\h寄容状态监视系统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.88,sign_monitor,PA,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fax0.2\c&H2E73D3&\blur0.7\pos(1234.8,654)\frz3.2}凸型因子脉冲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.88,sign_monitor,PA,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fax0.2\c&H2E73D3&\blur0.7\frz3.2\pos(1250.8,697.2)}凹型因子脉冲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.88,sign_monitor,,0,0,0,,{\c&H38404F&\pos(1297.2,398)\fax0.2}狂暴化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.88,sign_monitor,,0,0,0,,{\c&H38404F&\fs20\fax0.2\pos(1288,383.6)}雄蕊连接中断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.30,Default,7,0,0,0,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.39,Default,8,0,0,0,,在这节骨眼上时间用尽了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.53,Default,56,0,0,0,,广！零贰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.49,Default,56,0,0,0,,快回话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.65,Default,56,0,0,0,,喂　广！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.29,Default,15,0,0,0,,广...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:20.04,Default,15,0,0,0,,广死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.29,Default,56,0,0,0,,莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.75,Default,56,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.50,Default,666,0,0,0,,喂　广　你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.59,Default,390,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.46,Default,196,0,0,0,,那流言是真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.26,Default,556,0,0,0,,得快点去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:34.05,Default,326,0,0,0,,不止这样　这么下去的话墙壁也会被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.80,Default,214,0,0,0,,得...得阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.62,Default,15,0,0,0,,没能说出口...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.10,Default,15,0,0,0,,没能说出口让他别开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.27,Default,56,0,0,0,,振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.90,Default,56,0,0,0,,现在不是哭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.73,Default,56,0,0,0,,现在要考虑的是我们自己的性命！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.91,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是么... 我已经死了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.92,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能做的　我已经都做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:10.09,Default,703,0,0,0,,你又打算这样自我满足然后放弃么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.92,Default,703,0,0,0,,也对搭档的话充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:14.92,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.14,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这一定已经是我的极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.97,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和我们分开的时候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:26.10,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再说了　零贰就算没有我也一定可以继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.94,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她一直都是这么过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.44,Default,703,0,0,0,,广　你觉得这样就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.28,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我最后开动了 FRANXX
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.86,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给大家派上了用场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.24,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已经没有遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.37,Default,703,0,0,0,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.54,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.04,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}零贰...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.88,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是来为我送别的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.47,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多亏了你　我取回了自己的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.51,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然不久　但我作为孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.23,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.57,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么你一副这么寂寞的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.58,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}诶...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.86,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道没能打倒它？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.00,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.60,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,混蛋... 区区一个怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:46.18,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手　零贰　你一个人是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.10,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么下去　连你也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.07,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么都这样了还要战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.95,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能因为我是怪物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:59.41,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一直都是这样过来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.95,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失去搭档后　一个人孤单地...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:08.33,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没法独力飞翔　连你也是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.33,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直都是一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.71,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都怪这两支角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.68,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我到底在干些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.68,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}眼前的零贰明明这么痛苦着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.69,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.69,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想再次和你共同驾驶鹤望兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.69,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我的翅膀...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.99,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是为你而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.52,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Dar... ling？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.69,Default,16,0,0,0,,我是你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.15,Default,16,0,0,0,,不会让你孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:05.07,Default,56,0,0,0,,广... 他活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.08,Default,15,0,0,0,,广...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.70,Default,7,0,0,0,,广的生命指标恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.70,sign_monitor,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H2158B3&\frz0.7442\fax-0.6\pos(744,78)\b\fs35}\h   代号 016\N生命指标测量系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:10.70,sign_monitor,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H2158B3&\fax-0.6\b\pos(532,502)\fs35\frz356.1}\h   代号 002\N生命指标测量系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.37,Default,8,0,0,0,,这到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.21,Default,7,0,0,0,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.88,Default,556,0,0,0,,又变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.51,Default,326,0,0,0,,让它变形就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.97,Default,390,0,0,0,,你在发什么呆　莓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.39,Default,196,0,0,0,,机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.10,Default,214,0,0,0,,这次轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.47,Default,666,0,0,0,,我们也来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:33.52,Default,56,0,0,0,,再给鹤望兰创造一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.23,Default,15,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.45,Default,15,0,0,0,,广！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:48.32,Default,15,0,0,0,,零贰！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.20,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,要飞咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.16,Default,16,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.58,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,用我们的翅膀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.79,Default,16,0,0,0,,用咱们的翅膀！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:28.03,Default,090,0,0,0,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:33.04,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,要是他的话　说不定能实现零贰的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:36.29,Default,16,0,0,0,,零贰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:37.54,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:42.17,Default,16,0,0,0,,我找到了另一个驾驶 FRANXX 的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:45.01,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,嗯？是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:49.68,Default,16,0,0,0,,我想成为你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.06,Default,16,0,0,0,,虽说不知道下次时会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:59.56,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling 的话　无论是下次还是下下次肯定都没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:02.15,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,教室の窓越しにぼんやりと空に問う
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.18,0:23:02.15,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,透过教室的窗户玻璃　心不在焉地向天空叩问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.07,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是被称作「比翼鸟」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:07.82,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,「何のため僕は生きているの？」　わかんないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.15,0:23:07.82,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,「活在世上究竟有什么意义？」　实在搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:06.07,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}据说这种鸟只有一支翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.82,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雄性和雌性靠在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:14.62,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,教科書の余白に書いた理想の僕は
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.65,0:23:14.62,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,曾经在课本的角落里写过　未来的我绝对...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:11.95,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无论比谁都飞得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.04,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我能成为你的翅膀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:17.83,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,大人達の言いなりじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.62,0:23:17.83,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,不是对大人们的指示言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:23.92,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,飛ぶ鳥のような自由があって
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.83,0:23:23.92,ED - ZH - ep6,,0,0,0,,而是要能像飞鸟一样自由自在地飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:20.79,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算会燃尽我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.34,Default,16,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也会永远在你身旁给你依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:30.38,ED - JP - ep6,,0,0,0,,夢を見せたくせに　叶えれる力を
